Command: OUTPut{ch}:STATe {state}
Description: This command sets or queries the output state of the specified channel. When enabled (ON), the signal is present at the output connector. When disabled (OFF), the output is disconnected and the connector is at ground potential.
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:IMPedance {impedance}
Description: Set output impedance (50 ohm or high-Z)
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:POLarity {polarity}
Description: Set output polarity
Category: Output

Command: SOURce{ch}:FUNCtion:SHAPe {shape}
Description: Set the waveform shape/function
Category: Waveform

Command: SOURce{ch}:FUNCtion:SHAPe USER{n}
Description: Set output to user-defined arbitrary waveform
Category: Waveform

Command: SOURce{ch}:FUNCtion:RAMP:SYMMetry {percent}
Description: Set ramp symmetry percentage (0-100%)
Category: Waveform

Command: SOURce{ch}:PULSe:DCYCle {percent}
Description: Set square/pulse duty cycle (0.001-99.999%)
Category: Waveform

Command: SOURce{ch}:FREQuency:FIXed {freq}
Description: This command sets or queries the output frequency for the specified channel. The frequency is specified in Hertz (Hz). The available frequency range depends on the instrument model and selected waveform type.
Category: Frequency

Command: SOURce{ch}:FREQuency:MODE {mode}
Description: Set frequency mode
Category: Frequency

Command: SOURce{ch}:PULSe:PERiod {period}
Description: Set pulse period in seconds
Category: Frequency

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:AMPLitude {amplitude}
Description: Set peak-to-peak amplitude
Category: Amplitude

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:OFFSet {offset}
Description: Set DC offset voltage
Category: Amplitude

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:HIGH {level}
Description: Set high voltage level
Category: Amplitude

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:LOW {level}
Description: Set low voltage level
Category: Amplitude

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:UNIT {unit}
Description: Set voltage units
Category: Amplitude

Command: SOURce{ch}:PHASe:ADJust {phase}
Description: Set phase in degrees (-180 to +180)
Category: Phase

Command: SOURce{ch}:AM:DEPTh {depth}
Description: Set AM modulation depth (0-100%)
Category: Modulation

Command: SOURce{ch}:AM:INTernal:FREQuency {freq}
Description: Set AM internal modulation frequency
Category: Modulation

Command: SOURce{ch}:FM:DEViation {deviation}
Description: Set FM frequency deviation
Category: Modulation

Command: SOURce{ch}:PM:DEViation {deviation}
Description: Set PM phase deviation in degrees
Category: Modulation

Command: SOURce{ch}:FSKey:FREQuency {freq}
Description: Set FSK hop frequency
Category: Modulation

Command: SOURce{ch}:BURSt:MODE {mode}
Description: Set burst mode type
Category: Burst

Command: SOURce{ch}:BURSt:NCYCles {count}
Description: Set number of burst cycles (1-1000000 or INFinity)
Category: Burst

Command: SOURce{ch}:BURSt:TDELay {delay}
Description: Set burst delay time
Category: Burst

Command: SOURce{ch}:FREQuency:STARt {freq}
Description: Set sweep start frequency
Category: Sweep

Command: SOURce{ch}:FREQuency:STOP {freq}
Description: Set sweep stop frequency
Category: Sweep

Command: SOURce{ch}:SWEep:TIME {time}
Description: Set sweep time
Category: Sweep

Command: SOURce{ch}:SWEep:MODE {mode}
Description: Set sweep mode (auto or manual)
Category: Sweep

Command: SOURce{ch}:SWEep:SPACing {spacing}
Description: Set sweep spacing (linear or logarithmic)
Category: Sweep

Command: TRIGger:SEQuence:SOURce {source}
Description: Set trigger source
Category: Trigger

Command: TRIGger:SEQuence:TIMer {period}
Description: Set internal trigger timer period
Category: Trigger

Command: TRIGger:SEQuence:SLOPe {slope}
Description: Set external trigger slope
Category: Trigger

Command: *SAV {memory}
Description: Save setup to memory location (1-4)
Category: System

Command: *RCL {memory}
Description: Recall setup from memory location (1-4)
Category: System

Command: OUTPut{ch}:PATH {path}
Description: Set output signal path
Category: Output

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:AMPLitude {amplitude}
Description: Set output amplitude
Category: Output

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:OFFSet {offset}
Description: Set output DC offset
Category: Output

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:HIGH {level}
Description: Set output high voltage level
Category: Output

Command: SOURce{ch}:VOLTage:LEVel:IMMediate:LOW {level}
Description: Set output low voltage level
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:FILTer {type}
Description: Set filter type for signal path (requires Option AC)
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:FILTer:BPASs:RANGe {range}
Description: Set band pass filter frequency range
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut:OFF {state}
Description: Enable/disable 'All Outputs Off' control
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:ATTenuator:A1 {value}
Description: Set A1 attenuator value in dB (Band Pass Filter path)
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:ATTenuator:A2 {value}
Description: Set A2 attenuator value in dB (Band Pass Filter path)
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:ATTenuator:A3 {value}
Description: Set A3 attenuator value in dB (Band Pass Filter path)
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:ATTenuator:DAC {power}
Description: Set DAC output power level in dBm (AC output mode)
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:SVALue:ANALog:STATe {value}
Description: Set output condition when stopped
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:SVALue:MARKer{m} {value}
Description: Set marker output condition when stopped
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:WVALue:ANALog:STATe {value}
Description: Set output condition when waiting for trigger
Category: Output

Command: OUTPut{ch}:WVALue:MARKer{m} {value}
Description: Set marker output condition when waiting for trigger
Category: Output

Command: WLISt:WAVeform:NEW "{name}",{length},{type}
Description: Create a new waveform in memory
Category: Waveform

Command: WLISt:WAVeform:DATA "{name}",{offset},{size},{data}
Description: Set waveform data
Category: Waveform

Command: WLISt:WAVeform:DATA? "{name}",{offset},{size}
