Category: Video_Plugin

Command: LVS:EXPort:FILE {filename}
Description: Set export file path for image data
Category: Video_Plugin

Command: LVS:ENCoding:CBITs {bits}
Description: Set encoding color bits (6, 8, or 10 bit)
Category: Video_Plugin

Command: LVS:ENCoding:CMODe {state}
Description: Enable/disable compatibility mode
Category: Video_Plugin

Command: LVS:ENCoding:TYPE {type}
Description: Set encoding type (JEIDA or VESA)
