Command: LVS:FILE {filename}
Description: Set bitmap image file path
Category: Video_Plugin

Command: LVS:FRATe {rate}
Description: Set frame rate (1-144 Hz)
Category: Video_Plugin

Command: LVS:HRESolution {pixels}
